<inglise> (e) the quantities in each store. </inglise>
<eesti> e) igas laos olevad kogused. </eesti>
<inglise> Authorised primary processors must be in possession of certificates of delivery or take-over from the supplier or consignee concerned or other equivalent document accepted by the Member State covering all consignments of straw and fibre entering or leaving the undertaking and not covered by a contract or commitment as referred to in Article 5. </inglise>
<eesti> Heakskiidetud esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlejatel peab olema k&otilde;ikide ettev&otilde;ttesse saabuvate ja sealt v&auml;ljaviidavate saadetiste kohta, mis ei ole h&otilde;lmatud artiklis 5 osutatud lepingu v&otilde;i kohustusega, tarnesertifikaat v&otilde;i &uuml;lev&otilde;tmissertifikaat asjaomaselt tarnijalt v&otilde;i kaubasaajalt v&otilde;i muu samav&auml;&auml;rne liikmesriigi kinnitatud dokument. </eesti>
