<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Before 1 January of the marketing year concerned, sale/purchase or processing contracts covering straw may be transferred to an authorised primary processor other than the one who originally concluded the contract, with the signed agreement of the farmer and of the authorised primary processors transferring the contract between them. </inglise>
